title: MOROCCANOIL Gold Glimmer Shine 3.4oz
description: Moroccanoil glimmer shine is a finishing spray that attracts and reflects light to give hair a gorgeous gloss. Infused with argan oil, vitamins and antioxidants, it creates an invisible veil of luminous shine and protects hair against environmental elements such as sun, salt water and chlorine. Glimmer shine can also be used to enhance color and highlights, adding the perfect touch to any style.

title: Herstyler Classic Zebra Hair Straightener
description: For all the animal's print lovers! HerStyler brought to you a wild stylish Zebra print Hair Straightener. This product is the perfect combination between high quality Straightener and fashionable accessory Zebra Classic Features: 100% One inch ceramic plates for a safe use. Faster heat-up time than conventional straightening iron. On / Off switch and light weight. Hot and ready to use in 30 seconds. Ergonomic design makes it comfortable to use. Ultra-light: the body of the straightener is constructed using light-weight, high-strength composite materials commonly used in the aerospace industry. High concentration of negative ions cuts straightening time in half. Can be used on any type of texture of hair, 1 year warranty and dual voltage: 110V - 220V.
